description: The all new Raspberry Pi PI500 Is Here and better than Ever! A Full Arm Based PC inside of a Keyboard? Yes it is! The Pi500 offers more performance and More Ram! Quad-core 64-bit Arm Cortex-A76 processor, 8GB LPDDR4X SDRAM, 2 micro HDMI ports (supports up to 4Kp60), 2 USB 3.0 ports, 1 USB 2.0 ports, Gigabit Ethernet port and More! Plus they also Released a New 15.6” Raspberry Pi Monitor!
